{
  "stem": "19807.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 82.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, no question about my mother and my father.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But we were so closely and so attached to it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they came to the station.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And of course-- and I-- I can't forget that, my mother running alongside the train.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, until today when there is a scene with- with trains, with stations, I always get very shook up.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was-- But then also we were-- we had a lot of-- a lot of joy in that.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were now embarking on a tremendous adventure.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We're children.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Imagine, I was not even 14.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I celebrated my 14th birthday in Israel.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And those children were my playmates or my-- my classmates.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we're all together and looking forward to a new life.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were two adults who were put in the train that they were able to leave with us.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was the entire supervision.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I don't know the whole way.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were like supervisors.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But they were also granted visas and papers and all this.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And and I think one of-- one of them was able to leave very quickly because he was with Turkish citizens some kind of way.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But there were two male supervisors that-- that oversaw this group of about 42 children.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[SIGHS] It took us like almost 24 hours to get to Istanbul, because I don't know the exact amount of time that-- from Plovdiv to Istanbul.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But also we stayed at the-- at the boundary.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We-- they kept us there for quite a few hours until they cleared papers and all this.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then when we arrived to Istanbul, we met with the representative of the Jewish community.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Immediately they ushered us into a pensione on the Asian side.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
